{"tid":880992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳志健生日　張曦雯唐詩詠陪飲酒","createTime":"2018-10-29T06:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:48:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50eaba48e7b34d7f80b468ad1e1a401e7c428457","tid":880992,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"藝人陳志健（Otto）尋日（27日）37歲生日，不過佢就同劇組飛咗去澳洲為新劇《解決師》拍外景，所以就要喺當地過生日。Otto喺社交網上載一張獲拍檔唐詩詠、張曦雯同佢慶生合照，見到佢哋又飲酒同食甜品，相當開心！Otto開心留言：「多謝兩位美女，生日，澳洲，解決師。」一班網民都話有兩位靚女陪過生日，難怪Otto都舉起V字手勢，認真令人葡萄！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181028/photo/bkn-20181028044617820-1028_00862_001_01b.jpg?20181028073733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181028%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181028044617820-1028_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20181028073733&h=1c3f2ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181028/bkn-20181028044617820-1028_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181028%2Fbkn-20181028044617820-1028_00862_001.html&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=867d9b5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181028/bkn-20181028044617820-1028_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f71f753dbd8ec2f42893e320ad69c1f48312c5be","tid":880992,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"K歌之王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7988c25e5203d2256f13b627afc98b1d80b7ed","tid":880992,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f71f753dbd8ec2f42893e320ad69c1f48312c5be","tid":880992,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"K歌之王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"